-- Wal-Mart May Hire Another X5 Russian Executive, Kommersant Says
-- B y   I l y a   K h r e n n i k o v
-- 2012-02-15T04:55:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-15/wal-mart-may-hire-another-x5-russian-executive-kommersant-says.html
Wal-Mart Stores Inc. may hire
Ekaterina Ishevskaya, a former commercial director at  Russia ’s
 X5 Retail Group NV (FIVE) , after appointing X5 ex-CEO Lev Khasis senior
vice president last year,  Kommersant  reported.  Ishevskaya will be in charge of global brands purchases for
Wal-Mart, the Moscow-based newspaper said, citing people it
didn’t identified. Both executives will also help the U.S.
retailer enter the Russian market, Kommersant said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ilya Khrennikov in Moscow at 
 ikhrennikov@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Viljoen at 
 jviljoen@bloomberg.net  